name: Human vs Alien
description:
Goal:
  • Defend the Main Citadel from Aliens while trying to destroy their UFO
Character Human:
  • Main Citadel: White House
  • The glutton (fat), throws a big burger, but slow walk,, wearing a beer hat. Skill: throw food.
  • Ronaldo (6 packs), runs slow, attacks close, runs fast to get close to the enemy then kick, extremely strong kick.
  • The nerd (thin), reads the spell to freeze the nearest opponents for 6 seconds.
  • Helicopter (non-gender) fly from the top of the map to the end of the map dropping multiple bombs to an enemy group.
